SONOFF TX Gen2 Smart Touch Wall Switch | T6 120 Type
Description:
【Matter Compatibility】Effortlessly integrate with major smart home platforms and synchronize with your existing Matter-enabled devices for a unified, connected experience.
【Apple Ecosystem Compatible】Works seamlessly with your entire Apple ecosystem - Siri, iPhone, iPad, and Apple Watch. Control your devices via app, voice, or smart scenes.
【Smart Scene】 Create personalized automation scenarios across both the SONOFF and Matter ecosystems for a truly synchronized smart home.
【Detach Relay Mode】After enabling this feature, the physical buttons are separated from the relay status. This effectively prevents the smart light from going offline due to physical button operations, ensuring the smart light remains controllable at all times.
【Night Switch Locator】Features an LED indicator, making the switch easy to find in the dark. You can adjust the brightness of the light to suit your preference, ensuring it won't disturb your rest.

SONOFF Zigbee/Thread USB Dongle | Dongle Plus MG24
Description:
【Based on EFR32MG24】Power with the advanced EFR32MG24 chip, offering richer resources and higher performance to deliver faster automation processing and stable sub-device control.
【Enhanced Antenna Gain】Default 3dBi antenna gain, optimized up to 4.5dBi for stronger signal strength and wider coverage.
【Wide Platform Compatibility】Works seamlessly with multiple open-source platforms such as Home Assistant, Zigbee2MQTT, and more—perfect for open-source enthusiasts.
【Easy Firmware Flashing】Effortlessly flash different firmware using the SONOFF Dongle Flasher, enabling versatile roles and flexible usage.
【Include USB Extension Cable】Allows flexible connection to your host device while minimizing Zigbee 3.0 electromagnetic interference for better signal range.
Note : Use Dongle Flasher Web tool or Add-on to flash other firmware faster. Switch to other device types in 1minute.
Web Tool: https://dongle.sonoff.tech/sonoff-dongle-flasher/
Add-on: https://github.com/iHost-Open-Source-Project/hassio-ihost-addon/tree/master/hassio-ihost-sonoff-dongle-flasher

Name: SONOFF Dongle Max Zigbee/Thread PoE Dongle | Dongle-M
Description:
【High-Performance Chipset】Built on the powerful combination of EFR32MG24 +ESP32D0WDR2, Dongle Max delivers outstanding processing capability and rock-solid stability. Give you more performance headroom and future expansion possibilities.
【Flexible Connectivity Options】Supports Ethernet, Wi-Fi, and USB connections, giving you the freedom to deploy Dongle Max wherever it fits best. Even when your Dongle is far from the router, wireless access keeps it connected.
【Web-Based Management Interface】Access a dedicated web console that brings together device status, settings, logs, and alerts — all in one place. Monitor uptime, troubleshoot, or fine-tune behavior without command lines.
【Easy Firmware Management】Switch or update firmware right from the web interface — no disassembly or manual flashing required. Whether using it as a Zigbee coordinator, router, or Thread RCP, Dongle Max makes it simple.
【Reliable Build Quality】Equipped with 5dBi dual adjustable antennas for enhanced 360° signal coverage. The aluminum housing is built to last, tested with 24-hour salt spray, and certified by CE, FCC, and RoHS — ensuring long-term reliability and peace of mind.

Name: SONOFF CAM Outdoor Smart  Security Camera | CAM-B1P
Description:
【IP65 Weatherproof Design】IP65-rated waterproof and dustproof design, making it perfect for use in the outdoor environment.
【180° Horizontal Pan Control with 2K HD Resolution】Covers a wider area with a rotatable lens for fewer blind spots and more comprehensive monitoring.  Featuring 2K HD resolution, capture every detail with sharp, high-definition video for enhanced security and surveillance clarity.
【AI Human Detection & Smart Tracking】Accurately detects and follows human movement in real time, reducing false alerts and enhancing responsiveness.
【Full-Color Night Vision】CAM-B1P offers different night vision modes - Full-Color, Infrared (Black and White),  and Smart Night Vision, to ensure clear visibility in any lighting condition. 
【Preset Position Monitoring】Set and switch to specific viewpoints instantly to keep a close eye on key zones.

Name: SONOFF Zigbee Smart Roller Shutter Switch | MINI-ZBRBS
Description:
【Mini Size】This product is compact and perfectly compatible with various small-sized wall-mounted junction boxes, including the European standard 60/80 junction box.
【Precise Percentage Adjustment】Control indoor lighting according to your needs, enhancing comfort and energy efficiency while adapting flexibly to different scenarios.
【Zigbee Signal Booster】MINI-ZBRBS acts as a Zigbee router device, which helps extend your Zigbee network. Enjoy a stronger signal and improved reliability across your entire smart home.
【Zigbee Local Scene】Once configured via your Zigbee hub, scenes are executed locally within your home network, ensuring immediate response even when your internet is offline.
【Calibration of Curtain Operation】Reduce hardware inaccuracies and extend the lifespan of your smart curtains.

SONOFF Zigbee Smart Roller Shutter Switch | MINI-ZBRBS - 2 Pack
SONOFF Zigbee Smart Roller Shutter Switch | MINI-ZBRBS - 4 Pack
SONOFF Matter Over WiFi Smart Wall Switch | Orb-MW1
Description:
【Matter Compatibility】With Matter protocol support, Orb-MW1 ensures seamless integration with Apple Home, Amazon Alexa, Google Home, SmartThings, etc. Allowing you to work with other brands of Matter devices and build a unified smart home setup.
【 Detach Relay Mode】With this function enabled, you can still remotely control your smart devices through "Smart Scenes" even when the physical switch is turned off. And if the device goes offline, the physical switch instantly resumes full control.
【LAN Control】Even if there is no Internet, the switch can be used with local control.
【Smart Scene】Works seamlessly with SONOFF sensors, switches, and other devices, creating a fully connected smart ecosystem for a cohesive experience.
 【Compatible Accessories】Orb-MW1 is compatible with SONOFF Fusion Series Switch Frames (Orb-2/3 Gang, sold separately), allowing flexible vertical or horizontal installation.

Name: SONOFF Zigbee Smart Wall Switch (No Neutral Required) | Orb-ZBW1L
Description:
【No Neutral Wire Needed】Orb-ZBW1L works without a neutral wire, making it perfect for older homes, for effortless integration into your existing setup.
【Zigbee Hub Compatible】Supports Zigbee hubs using the Zigbee 3.0 protocol, like SONOFF iHost, NSPanel Pro, ZBBridge-P, ZBBridge-U, ZBDongle-E, ZBDongle-P, Echo 4th Gen, Echo Show 2nd, and Echo Plus 2nd, SmartThings V3 hub.
【Optimized for Low-Wattage Bulbs】Specially designed to handle low-power loads as small as 3W with no anti-flicker module required. Enjoy stable, flicker-free operation even with modern LED and energy-saving bulbs – maximum compatibility, zero headaches.  
【Seamless Integration with Home Assistant】Easily add to Home Assistant for your home automation through ZHA or Zigbee2MQTT( Zigbee Dongle is required, e.g. SONOFF ZBDongle-P/ ZBDongle-E).
【Advanced Smart Scene Capabilities】Easily set countdown, schedule, or loop timers for personalized automation. Voice control is supported with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant, enabling hands-free operation. You can also trigger other Zigbee devices based on the switch state, creating a truly intelligent and automated smart home experience.

Note 1: The Zigbee Hub is needed.
Note 2: Orb-ZBW1L is a Zigbee End-Device.

Description:
【Crystal-Clear 1080P Full HD Live View】Enjoy sharp, detailed video quality with 1080P Full HD resolution. Whether it’s daytime or night, every scene is captured clearly for better surveillance, evidence collection, and peace of mind. See every detail. Miss nothing.
【Customizable Alert Zones – Focus on What Matters】Define specific activity zones within the camera’s field of view to monitor only the areas that matter to you. Adjust motion sensitivity to reduce false alarms and receive relevant alerts only.
【AI Human Detection – Smarter Motion Alerts】Equipped with advanced AI-based human detection, the camera sends alerts only when a person is detected, ignoring irrelevant motion like pets or wind-blown leaves. This minimizes false notifications and helps you focus on real threats.
【Privacy Protection – Your Space, Your Rules】Protect your personal space with multiple privacy features: Sleep Mode to turn off video monitoring entirely; Custom Privacy Zones to block out sensitive areas from being recorded.
【Flexible Storage Options – Cloud or Local】You can securely save your recordings either to the cloud with the optional Camera Plan (sold separately) or locally using a TF (microSD) card (sold separately), giving you flexible and convenient storage choices.

SONOFF NSPanel Pro Smart Home Control Panel 86 Type
Description:
【All-in-One Control】NSPanel Pro supports unlimited SONOFF devices—from smart lights and cameras to sensors and switches. Future SONOFF devices will also be compatible, ensuring long-term scalability.
【Built-in Zigbee Hub】Easily batch-add Zigbee devices via the touchscreen. The standard Zigbee 3.0 protocol ensures stable connections and wider coverage. The added sub-devices can be voice-controlled via Alexa, Google Home, and more.
【Smart Security】Create up to 3 custom security modes with different arming configurations. Once armed, the triggered sensor will activate an alarm on the panel and send instant alerts to your phone.
【Temperature Control】Select the temperature source (e.g., TH Elite) and control devices (e.g., MINIR4M, ZBMINIL2) to build a personalized thermostat system that keeps your space comfortable.
【Live Camera Monitoring】NSPanel Pro functions as a real-time display for the supported cameras. Monitor key areas like the living room, garage, or bedroom directly from the panel at any time.

SONOFF NSPanel Pro Smart Home Control Panel 86 Type - White

【Web Access Shortcut】Save your favorite websites directly on the panel. Whether you’re streaming music, watching videos, or browsing tips, launch them instantly with one tap.

Name: SONOFF 4CHR3 & 4CHPROR3 4-gang Wi-Fi Smart Switch with RF Control
Description:
【WiFi Connected, No Hub Required】Directly connect to your home network via WiFi protocol, eliminating the need for additional gateways. Control devices remotely through the eWeLink app anytime, anywhere.
【Dry Contact for Smart Upgrades】Transform traditional devices into smart systems! Perfect for retrofitting garage doors, motorized curtains, etc.
【Voice Control with Alexa & Google Home】Seamlessly integrate with popular smart ecosystems. Use voice commands to operate devices hands-free – "Alexa, turn off the garage light" or "Hey Google, close the living room curtains".
【10A High-Load Capacity per Channel】Supports both DC/AC input (100-240V) with robust 10A load handling per channel. Safely control appliances like water heaters, pumps, and HVAC systems.
【DIN Rail Installation Ready】Designed for standard DIN rail mounting. ensuring a clean and professional layout. This minimizes clutter and improves accessibility for maintenance.

Name: SONOFF BASICR4 Wi-Fi Smart Switch
Description:
【Equipped with ESP32 – Smarter Core, Better Performance】Equipped with the new-generation ESP32 chip, BASICR4 delivers faster response, more stable connectivity, and enhanced processing power — all while keeping it cost-effective for your smart home setup.
【Magic Switch Mode – Smart Even When Wall Switch is Off】Thanks to its unique Magic Switch Mode, you can still control your lights from the app, even if a traditional wall switch has been turned off. Enjoy continuous remote access and automation.
【Built-in eWeLink-Remote Gateway – Unlock Local Two-Way Control】As a gateway device for eWeLink-Remote, BASICR4 lets you pair with S-Mate2, R5, and other remote sub-devices. Set up two-way or multi-way control, and enjoy low-latency local control without relying on Wi-Fi.
【Group Control – Smarter Management of Multiple Devices】Easily group your devices by room or scene, and control multiple switches simultaneously via app. Save time and simplify your daily routines.
【Certified Safety with Real-Time Thermal Protection】Features a built-in temperature sensor that continuously monitors internal heat levels. Automatically cuts off power in case of overheating, protecting your home from risks like deformation, fire, or exposure of live wires. Certified by CE, FCC, ETL, and more.

Name: SONOFF DUALR3/DUALR3 Lite Dual Relay Two Way Power Metering Smart Switch
Description:
【Motor Mode – Smart Roller Shades & Curtain Motor Control】Easily upgrade your electric curtains, blinds, or roller shades into smart devices. Use app, voice, or automation to control your window coverings remotely—perfect for modern smart homes.
【Switch Mode – Dual-Channel Smart Load Control】Control two electrical appliances independently with one device. Ideal for remotely managing lights, ceiling fans, coffee makers, and more via app, voice command, or automation. Perfect for building a flexible smart home control system.
【Dual-Channel Power Metering – Track Energy Usage】Each channel independently measures voltage, current, and power consumption, helping you manage and optimize energy usage. (Note: Not available in DUALR3 Lite)
【Two-Way Wall Switch Control – Flexible & Compatible】DUALR3 supports 6 types of external switch detection (e.g., rocker, momentary, SPDT), making it compatible with most traditional wall switches. Maintain manual wall switch control while upgrading to smart functionality.
【Certified Safety & Reliability】Built with safety in mind—certified by TÜV, CE, FCC, and RoHS standards. It delivers stable performance and peace of mind.

Name: SONOFF iFan04: Wi-Fi Ceiling Fan And Light Controller
Description:
【Smart Upgrade for Existing Systems】Directly replace traditional ceiling fan-light controllers with iFan04 to instantly upgrade to smart control capabilities, enabling app-based remote operation, automated scenarios, and precision scheduling functions.
【Dual Voltage Universal Compatibility】Compatible with global ceiling fan-light models supporting 100-130V (North American standard) and 220-240V (European/Asian standard) input voltages, covering over 90% of market-available configurations.
【Voice Command Integration】Works natively with Amazon Alexa and Google Home for hands-free voice control through simple vocal commands.
【Gateway-Free WiFi Connection】Built-in WiFi module enables direct eWeLink app connectivity without requiring additional hubs, supporting real-time control through iOS/Android devices from any location.
【Three-Stage Speed control】Precisely adjust fan speed with low/medium/high settings to keep your room comfortable.

Name: SONOFF MINIR2 – Two Way Smart Switch
Description:
【Two-Way Control – Smart Retrofit Without Changing Your Switch】Easily upgrade your existing lights with MINIR2, which fits discreetly inside the switch box. Enjoy full smart control while retaining manual physical switch operation — no visible changes needed.
【Open Device REST API – Seamless Home Automation Integration】Connect MINIR2 to your preferred home automation system like Home Assistant via LAN using its open REST API, enabling custom integrations and advanced control.
【Fully Featured Smart Switch】MINIR2 supports all essential functions: remote app control, scheduling, sharing with your family, and more. The perfect DIY smart switch for flexible, personalized setups.
【Smart Scenes Automation】Create automated scenes to trigger other smart devices, turning appliances on/off automatically based on your schedule or conditions, making your home truly intelligent.
【Hands-Free Voice Control】Compatible with Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, SmartThings, and Alice. Simply speak your command, and your devices respond instantly.

Name: SONOFF Smart Stackable Power Meter | SPM
Description:
【UP to 32 SPM-4Relays】One SPM-Main connects up to 32 SPM-4Relays. Each relay includes 4 isolated channels for organized and scalable device control.
【20A per Channel】Each channel supports up to 20 amps, making it ideal for high-power devices.
【Overload Protection】Automatically cuts off power during overloads to protect your devices and ensure system safety.
【MicroSD Storage】Store over 20 years of power data and up to 20,000 operation logs per device. Quickly export consumption reports via SD card.
【Power Monitoring】Track real-time current, voltage, and power usage through the eWeLink app for smarter energy management.

Name: SONOFF TH Elite Smart Temperature and Humidity Monitoring Switch | THR316D/THR320D
Description:
【20A Max Load with Dry Contact Output – Industrial & HVAC Ready】Supports up to 20A high load, and with dry contact output, making it ideal for controlling boilers, HVAC systems, industrial relays, and other non-voltage input equipment. Reliable performance for both residential and commercial automation.
【Built-in LCD Display – Real-Time Temp & Humidity Monitoring】Equipped with a clear LCD screen, it shows real-time temperature and humidity, updating every 5 seconds. Always stay informed of your environment without opening the app.
【6-Month Temperature & Humidity History – Hourly Accuracy, Exportable】Stores temperature and humidity data for up to 6 months, viewable by hour, day, or month. Data can be exported in .xlsx format for home comfort analysis.
【Smart Schedule Programming – Energy Saving with Home Comfort】Create up to 8 customized automation programs based on temperature, humidity, and time settings. Automatically turn devices on or off to reduce energy consumption and maintain a comfortable indoor environment all day long.
【Voice Control & Real-Time Query – Alexa, Google Assistant Supported】Use simple voice commands to query temperature or humidity, or to control connected appliances. Works seamlessly with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant for hands-free smart home control.

Name: SONOFF POW Elite Smart Power Meter Switch
Description:
【Real-Time Power Monitoring on LCD Display】Equipped with a clear LCD screen, POW Elite shows real-time power, voltage, current, and cumulative energy consumption directly on the device. No need to check your phone for instant readings.
【Supports Up to 20A Load – Ideal for More Appliances】Handles up to 20A of high-power electrical load, making it compatible with energy-demanding appliances like heaters, light systems, and more.
【6-Month Power Usage History – Hourly Accuracy & Exportable】Access and analyze your power consumption data with hour-level accuracy for the past 6 months. Easily export the data to Excel (.xlsx) right from the app—ideal for tracking usage or optimizing energy plans.
【Customizable Overload Protection – Safer Automation】Set thresholds for power, voltage, and current. POW Elite will automatically shut off the power if any preset limit is exceeded, ensuring the safety of your appliances and electrical system.
【All-in-One Smart Features – Full Control in Your Hands】Includes remote app control, voice control (Alexa & Google Assistant), timers, inching mode, and power-on state memory. Everything you need in a professional-grade smart energy meter.

Name: SONOFF POWR3 High Power Smart Switch
Description:
【25A / 5500W Output – Power Up Your Heavy Appliances】With a maximum output of 25A / 5500W, POWR3 is perfect for high-powered devices like water heaters, HVAC systems, and other equipment. Also ideal for use as a dedicated room-level energy meter.
【Real-Time Power Consumption Monitoring】Track active power, voltage, and current of connected appliances directly in the eWeLink app. Stay informed and manage electricity usage with accurate live data and historical insights.
【Built-in Overload Protection – Safety First】Automatically shuts off power when abnormal current or voltage is detected, helping to prevent short circuits, device damage, and fire hazards. Protect your appliances and your home.
【Remote On/Off Control – Anytime, Anywhere】Turn off your devices from anywhere with one tap on your phone. Helps to cut power, reduce energy bills, and ensure safety even when you're not home.
【Hands-Free Voice Control with Alexa, Google & More】Fully compatible with Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, SmartThings, and Alice. Just say the word to control your appliances—no hands needed.

Name: SONOFF TH Origin Smart Temperature and Humidity Monitoring Switch (TH10/16 Upgrade Version) | THR316/THR320
Description:
【Supports High Power Devices – Up to 20A Max Load】With 20A maximum output, this smart switch can handle high-power home appliances like heaters, dehumidifiers, or electric kettles. 
【6-Month Temperature & Humidity History – Exportable by Hour】Track temperature and humidity data hourly for the past 6 months. View trends by hour, day, or month, and export data as .xlsx files for easy analysis. Ideal for greenhouses, server rooms, or Fermentation rooms.
【Smart Schedule Programming – Energy Saving with Home Comfort】Create up to 8 customized automation programs based on temperature, humidity, and time settings. Automatically turn devices on or off to reduce energy consumption and maintain a comfortable indoor environment all day long.
【Voice Control with Alexa & Google Assistant】Hands-free control with your voice assistants. Just speak out your command, the device will turn on/off as you say, or check the temperature and humidity for you.
【Smart Scenes & Multi-Device Automation】Easily create smart scenes that trigger actions based on temperature, humidity, or device status (on/off/invert). Use TH Origin as a trigger or an action executor in your broader smart home ecosystem.

Name: SONOFF POW Origin Smart Power Meter Switch
Description:
【Real-Time Power Monitoring – Know Your Energy Usage】Monitor real-time power, current, voltage, and total energy consumption of connected appliances. Stay informed and take control of your electricity use with precise, live data.
【Supports High-Power Devices – Up to 16A Load】Built to handle up to 16A, POW Origin is compatible with a wide range of home appliances like heaters, light systems, and more. A smart choice for energy-intensive devices.
【6-Month Energy History – Exportable Data】Access and analyze historical power consumption data for the past 6 months, accurate to the hour. Easily export data to Excel (.xlsx) right from your phone for tracking or reporting.
【Built-in Overload Protection – Safer Appliance Control】Set thresholds for power, voltage, or current. When a limit is exceeded, the device will automatically shut off to prevent overloading and protect your appliances from damage.
【All-in-One Smart Switch Functionality】POW Origin includes remote app control, voice control (Alexa & Google Assistant), schedules, inching mode, and power-on state memory. The ultimate smart power switch for DIY automation.

Name: SONOFF S-MATE Extreme Switch Mate | S-MATE2
Description:
【Compact & Universal Compatibility – Fits Most Mounting Boxes】S-Mate2 features a slim, compact design that fits easily into EU/86 type or US 120 type electrical boxes, and works with a wide variety of physical switches — including rocker, push-button, or toggle switches. Seamless integration into existing switch setups.
【50M Reliable Local Control with “eWeLink-Remote”】Pair S-Mate2 with MINIR4 or other eWeLink-Remote gateway-enabled devices to enable up to 50 meters of stable local wireless control (no obstacles). No Wi-Fi required for communication—ideal for multi-room smart control.
【Designed for Versatile Scenarios – No Neutral? No Problem】Supports smart home solutions like two-way control, multi-way lighting, and no-neutral switch wiring setups. A powerful add-on for smart retrofitting without changing existing wiring—perfect for older homes and renovations.
【Up to 5 Years Battery Life – Low Maintenance】Powered by a CR2477 coin battery, S-Mate2 is built for long-term use. With optimized energy efficiency, you can enjoy up to 5 years of battery life (lab tested). Less hassle, more convenience.

Name: SONOFF MINI Extreme Wi-Fi Smart Switch MINIR4
Description:
【Ultra-Compact Design】MINIR4’s super tiny size fits easily into various mounting boxes, including the smallest European standard boxes, making installation quick and hassle-free.
【Equipped with ESP32 Chip – High-Performance Smart Core】MINIR4 features the powerful ESP32 chip, delivering faster response times, more stable connectivity, and enhanced processing power. Designed for reliable and long-lasting performance, it ensures seamless smart home automation and smooth device control.
【Flexible External Switch Compatibility】Supports multiple switch types such as momentary switches, door exit switches, SPDT switches, latching switches, and even dry contact sensors for versatile control options.
【Detach Relay Mode for Independent Control】With the unique “detach relay” mode, the external switch state and the relay state operate independently. Pressing the external switch won’t affect the relay’s on/off status, providing more flexible control.
【eWeLink-Remote Gateway Function】MINIR4 acts as a smart switch and gateway for “eWeLink-Remote”. Pair with sub-devices like R5 and S-MATE to enable local remote control via eWeLink-Remote signals, enhancing your smart home network.

Name: SONOFF MINI Extreme Wi-Fi Smart Switch (Matter-enabled) | MINIR4M
Description:
【Universal Compatibility with Matter Ecosystems】MINIR4M is a Matter-certified smart switch, enabling seamless integration with Apple Home, Amazon Alexa, Google Home, SmartThings, and other Matter-enabled ecosystems. No more juggling between apps — now you can control all your smart devices in one unified platform, regardless of brand. Perfect for building a future-proof smart home.
【Ultra-Compact Design – Fits in Tight Spaces】Designed for flexibility, the MINIR4M fits easily into standard 86-type and EU electrical mounting boxes, making it ideal for both new installations and retrofitting existing switches. Upgrade your wall switch in minutes.
【Works with Multiple External Switch Types】MINIR4M supports momentary switches, SPDT (two-way) switches, and latching switches. Enjoy the freedom to combine manual control with automation.
【Turn Everyday Devices into Smart Appliances】Easily upgrade your lamp, fan, and other small appliances into smart devices with the SONOFF MINIR4M. Enjoy remote control, automation, and voice assistant integration — all from your favorite smart home app. From conventional to connected, without changing your existing appliances.
【Certified Safety – TÜV, CE, and FCC Approved】MINIR4M is built with your safety in mind. It has passed TÜV, CE, and FCC certifications, ensuring reliable performance, electromagnetic compatibility, and electrical protection.

Name: SONOFF POW Ring Smart Power Meter | POWCT
Description:
【Split Core Current Transformer – Non-Invasive & Safe Monitoring】Measure current up to 100A with a split-core clamp design — no need to touch live wires. Just snap the CT sensor open or closed via side latches for quick and safe installation, ideal for both DIYers and professionals.
【Real-Time Energy Monitoring – Room or Circuit Level Insight】Install POWCT in your home’s electrical panel to monitor power usage by room, circuit, or heavy-duty appliances. Identify energy waste, optimize power consumption, and gain full control over your electricity usage.
【Track Exported Power to the Grid – Optimize Solar Efficiency】POWCT is more than just an energy monitor—it’s a smart solution for tracking bidirectional power flow, including energy exported back to the grid. When integrated with solar inverters or battery storage systems, it provides real-time data on surplus electricity generation, helping you maximize self-consumption, reduce waste, and improve your return on investment from solar power.
【6-Month Historical Power Data – Auto Save & Exportable】Review hour-level electricity data for up to 6 months, and you can export it as files for energy analysis or reporting.
【Dry Contact Relay – Contactors & Load Control Supported】Equipped with a 2A dry contact output, POWCT can be connected to an external contactor to switch large electrical loads on or off. Perfect for industrial applications or smart energy management systems.

Name: SONOFF Micro Zigbee USB Smart Adaptor | ZBMicro
Description:
【Smart USB Control via Zigbee – Remote Access & Automation】Turn ordinary USB-powered devices into smart ones. As a Zigbee USB adapter, this device lets you remotely control USB devices, set smart timers, build automated scenes.
【Supports Up to 36W Fast Charging – Safer, Smarter Power Management】Pair it with your original fast-charging adapter to enable up to 36W output. You can schedule charging time to avoid overcharging, prolong battery life, and save energy—ideal for night-time charging or unattended device management.
【Turbo Mode with Extended Coverage – Stronger Signal, Greater Reach】Boost your Zigbee network with Turbo Mode. This feature enhances Zigbee signal strength and coverage, ensuring more stable communication between your devices.
【USB 2.0 Data Transmission】Equipped with USB 2.0, it ensures data transmission, seamless connectivity, and wide compatibility with various devices, making setup and integration easier than ever.
【Seamless Integration with Home Assistant & OpenHAB】Effortlessly connect to major smart home platforms like Home Assistant (via ZHA or Zigbee2MQTT) and OpenHAB. Enjoy smooth Zigbee device pairing, simplified automation routines, and full ecosystem compatibility—perfect for DIY smart home enthusiasts and advanced users alike.

Name: SONOFF ZBMINI Extreme Zigbee Smart Switch ZBMINIR2
Description:
【Ultra-Compact Design – Fits EU/86/120-Type Mounting Boxes】The ZBMINIR2 smart switch features a miniature form factor that easily fits inside EU-type, 86-type, and 120-type electrical boxes. Perfect for tight installations and discreet smart upgrades. Ideal for both new builds and retrofits without altering your wall switch layout.
【External Switch Support – Works with Various Switch Types】Easily integrate with your existing switches! ZBMINIR2 supports a wide range of external switches, including momentary switches, door contact switches, SPDT switches, and rocker switches. Add smart functionality while keeping manual control.
【Zigbee Signal Booster – Expands Coverage & Connectivity】ZBMINIR2 not only acts as a Zigbee router device, but it also helps extend your Zigbee network by supporting up to 64 Zigbee end devices. Enjoy a stronger signal and improved reliability across your entire smart home.
【Smarten Up Your Lighting – Full Control at Your Fingertips】Easily turn your lights ON or OFF remotely and enjoy complete smart control over your lighting system. With individual device configuration and scene-based automation, you can personalize how your lights behave based on time, motion, or other connected devices.
【Open-Source Platform Friendly – Perfect for DIY enthusiasts】Built on the Zigbee 3.0 standard, ZBMINIR2 ensures broad compatibility and seamless integration with popular third-party platforms like Home Assistant  (via ZHA or Zigbee2MQTT)  and other open-source smart home systems. Perfect for DIY enthusiasts and advanced users looking to build a flexible, reliable home automation setup.

Name: SONOFF MINI Dry Wi-Fi Smart Switch | MINI-D
Description:
【Matter-Compatible – Cross-Platform Smart Home Integration】The SONOFF MINI-D is a Matter-certified smart switch, designed for seamless integration with Matter-enabled platforms, including Amazon Alexa, Google Home, Apple Home, Home Assistant, and more. Enjoy effortless control of smart devices from different brands, all through one unified ecosystem. Build a truly interoperable smart home with Matter technology.
【Flexible AC/DC Power Supply Support】Designed for versatility, the MINI-D supports powered by AC (100–240V) or DC (12–48V) power sources, enabling easy installation in residential, industrial, or custom control environments. Perfect for various wiring scenarios and locations.
【Dry Contact Output – Supports NO & NC Configurations】The SONOFF MINI-D features dry contact output with both Normally Open (NO) and Normally Closed (NC) options, allowing flexible control of a wide range of signal-based systems. It’s ideal for operating boilers, garage door openers, access control panels, and other devices that rely on non-voltage triggering. Perfect for integrating smart control into traditional low-voltage or relay-based systems.
【Optimized for DC Low-Power Motors (Max 8W)】Specially engineered to control low-power DC motors or solenoid valves (up to 8W), the MINI-D offers an ideal solution for smart irrigation, motorized curtains, or gate systems that run on low-voltage DC circuits.
【Integrated with Contactor Control – Manage High-Power Loads Safely】When paired with a contactor, MINI-D allows a low-power control circuit to safely switch high-power electrical systems, such as industrial equipment or HVAC units. This not only increases safety and energy efficiency but also allows precise smart control over large loads.

Name: SONOFF Zigbee Human Presence Sensor | SNZB-06P
Description:
【Presence Detection】SNZB-06P based on 5.8GHz microwave radar, it can detect movement or stationary person. It automatically turns on the lights when you approach and keeps the lights on until you leave.
【Light Sensing】The built-in light detector ensures that the lights are only turned on when presence is detected in the dark, helping you save energy.
【Zigbee 3.0 Compatible】Supports Zigbee hubs using the Zigbee 3.0 protocol, like SONOFF NSPanel Pro, SONOFF iHost, SONOFF ZB Bridge Pro, SONOFF ZBDongle-E, and Echo Plus 2nd…
【Local Smart Scene】Scene linkage between Zigbee devices can be executed normally even if there is no internet connection.
【Support Multiple Platforms】Supporting Alexa, Google Home, Smartthings, Alice, IFTTT, and Home Assistant.

Note: SNZB-06P needs to be used with Zigbee Hub.
Attribute 1 value(s): Dim Gray, Dim Gray, White, White

Name: SONOFF POW Ring Smart Power Meter | POWCT
Description:

Name: Nest E Smart Thermostat Home Automation Heating Hot Water
Description:
No professional installation needed
The Nest Thermostat E is the ideal cost-cutting solution for your home. Most utility expenses come from keeping your home warm - it makes sense to take advantage of a smart device that works with your existing heating to run efficiently. This device doesn't need professional installation, so you can install it yourself and start saving right away.
It includes the Thermostat E and the Heat Link E. The Heat Link goes in the same place as your current thermostat, while the Thermostat E can be placed somewhere handy in your home.
Save tons on utilities
Download the easy-to-use Nest app on your smartphone and control your home's temperature, anytime and from anywhere. The Thermostat E knows when everyone's left the house and automatically turns the heating down, so you're not warming an empty house.
You can turn your heating back up from the app, so you can get your home nice and toasty by the time you get home from work, without leaving the heat on all day.
Sync up with Google Home
The Thermostat E is compatible with your Google Home, so you can ask your Google Assistant to turn down the heat if it's getting warm while you're cooking dinner.
Heat Link E
The Heat Link E is also included to sense the temperature in the house, so the Thermostat E can automatically adjust the heating when needed.
Don't worry about the Heat Link E sticking out like a sore thumb. This handy device comes in grey to complement any wall color.

Features

  • No professional installation needed to upgrade your home's heating
  • Save tons on utilities by taking advantage of the Nest app for iOS and Android
  • Sync up with Google Home and control the temperature with your voice
  • Heat Link E lets your device modulate the temperature automatically

Nest E Thermostat

  • Control your home heating from your smartphone or tablet
  • Responds to your touch
  • No hub required
  • Control via Google Home
  • Compatible with iOS / Android

Name: Philips Hue Solo Lightstrip | 5-Meter Smart LED | White & Colour Ambiance | Plug Type G
Description:
Philips Hue Solo Lightstrip: Transform Your Home with Vibrant Smart Lighting

Create a stunning atmosphere in any room with the Philips Hue Solo 5-Meter Smart LED lightstrip. This easy-to-install, bendable lightstrip offers brilliant white light and millions of colours, providing the perfect ambience for any occasion. Control it instantly with Bluetooth or unlock the full power of your smart home with a Hue Bridge (sold separately).

  • Brilliant RGBWW LEDs: Enjoy pure, vibrant colours and true, natural white light. This lightstrip uses a dedicated RGBWW LED for each colour and white, ensuring no blending for a richer, more accurate spectrum.
  • Powerful Light Output: With 1700 lumens, this 5-metre lightstrip provides a stunningly bright and uniform light, perfect for illuminating larger areas and creating a truly immersive environment.
  • Simple & Instant Installation: The lightstrip can be easily cut to fit your space and features a self-adhesive backing. Simply stick it to your desired surface, plug it in, and begin controlling it with the Philips Hue app.
  • Works with Smart Home Assistants: Control your lighting with just your voice. The lightstrip works with Alexa, Google Assistant, and Apple HomeKit, allowing you to turn lights on/off, dim them, or change colours with simple voice commands.
  • Seamless Smart Control: Connect with the Philips Hue app via Bluetooth for instant control of up to 10 lights in one room. Add a Hue Bridge to unlock features like away-from-home control, automations, and Matter compatibility.

Ultimate Ambiance with True Colours and Brilliant Light

The Philips Hue Solo lightstrip is engineered to deliver a truly brilliant and authentic lighting experience. Unlike lightstrips that blend primary colours to create white light, this model uses dedicated RGBWW LEDs, giving you access to 16 million colours and a full spectrum of white light—from warm to cool. With a powerful output of 1700 lumens, the light is bright and consistent across the entire 5-meter length, making it ideal for creating dramatic effects under cabinets, along ceilings, or in any other large area you wish to transform.

Designed for Effortless Use and Integration

This lightstrip is as easy to use as it is beautiful. The bendable and cuttable design allows you to perfectly customise the length for your space without any fuss. The included plug and adhesive backing mean you can have your new smart lighting installed and running in minutes. With Bluetooth connectivity, you can start controlling your lightstrip right out of the box using the Philips Hue app, without the need for a bridge. For a more expansive smart home system, simply add a Hue Bridge (sold separately) to gain access to advanced features like timers, automations, and control of up to 50 lights throughout your entire home. The lightstrip's compatibility with Matter ensures it integrates seamlessly with a wide range of other smart home devices.

Control It Your Way with Voice and App

The Philips Hue Solo lightstrip offers multiple ways to control your lighting. Use the Philips Hue app to create custom light scenes, set the mood with dynamic effects, or adjust the brightness to your liking. When connected to a Hue Bridge, you can integrate it with your favourite voice assistants, including Amazon Alexa, Apple HomeKit (Siri), and Google Assistant. Simple voice commands like "Alexa, turn on the lightstrip" or "Hey Google, set the lightstrip to blue" put you in complete control. With a two-year warranty and a long nominal lifetime of 25,000 hours, this lightstrip is a reliable and long-lasting addition to your smart home ecosystem.

Technical Specifications

  • Brand: Philips Hue
  • Type: Solo Lightstrip Base Kit
  • Length: 5 metres
  • Power Source: Mains (Plug Type G)
  • Light Source: LED (RGBWW)
  • Lumen Output: 1700 lm (at 4000K), 1500 lm (at 2700K)
  • Power Consumption: 20W (0.5W Standby)
  • Dimmable: Yes
  • Connectivity: Bluetooth and Zigbee (requires Hue Bridge for full functionality)
  • Compatibility: Works with Philips Hue App (iOS 16+), Amazon Alexa, Google Assistant, Apple HomeKit, Matter
  • IP Rating: IP20 (Indoor use only)
  • Cut-ability: Yes (but not extendable once cut)
  • Material: Silicone
  • What's in the Box: 1 x 5-metre lightstrip, 1 x Power Adapter (with Plug Type G)

WHAT’S IN THE BOX - Includes one 5-meter Solo lightstrip base kit with one plug to create extraordinary ambience anywhere in your home – from the living room to the bedrooms.
BRILLIANT LIGHT - Experience 1700 lumens of bright light.
TRUE COLORS AND WHITES - We believe RGB LEDs should never be blended to create white light. That’s why our lightstrips only use RGBWW LEDs for true colors and pure white light.
INSTALL IN AN INSTANT - Getting started couldn't be easier. Cut your lightstrips to fit into your space. Then stick it, plug it and use it. Keep in mind, once you cut it, you can't reconnect it.
PERFECT FOR LONG SURFACES - Ideal for larger areas, Solo lightstrip can help transform living rooms, bedrooms, ceilings, stairs, and more.
UNLOCK THE FULL POWER OF HUE - Add a Hue Bridge to enjoy automations, control from anywhere in the world, and a secure, stable connection that won’t drain your Wi-Fi. Use Matter to connect your smart home devices to your Hue smart lighting system.

Name: Blink Outdoor 4 | 1-Camera System | Wireless HD Smart Security Camera | 2-Year Battery Life
Description:
Blink Outdoor 4: Wireless, Weather-Resistant HD Security for Your Home

Protect your home with the new Blink Outdoor 4, a wireless HD smart security camera system that's easy to set up and built to last. With up to two years of battery life, enhanced motion detection, and seamless Alexa integration, you can monitor your property day and night, rain or shine, directly from your smartphone.

  • Two-Year Battery Life: Powered by two AA lithium batteries, the Outdoor 4 provides up to two years of continuous power, so you can forget about frequent battery changes.
  • 1080p HD Video & Night Vision: See, hear, and speak to visitors with clear 1080p HD live view, infrared night vision, and crisp two-way audio directly from the Blink app.
  • Enhanced Motion Detection: Receive faster alerts on your smartphone with dual-zone motion detection, allowing you to customise Activity Zones to monitor only the areas that matter to you.
  • Weather-Resistant Design: With an IP65 rating, the camera is designed to withstand the elements, operating in temperatures from -20°C to 45°C.
  • Works with Alexa: Arm and disarm your system, stream live video, and control your cameras with simple voice commands using a compatible Alexa-enabled device.

Be There from Anywhere with the Newest Generation Blink Camera

The Blink Outdoor 4 is the fourth generation of wireless smart security cameras, offering a significant upgrade in performance and features. Its wider 143° diagonal field of view captures more of your property than its predecessor, providing a more comprehensive view of your surroundings. The camera's enhanced image quality and improved low-light performance ensure you get a clearer picture both day and night. With the included Sync Module Core, this single-camera system gives you the foundation for a complete home security setup, all controlled from the intuitive Blink app on your smartphone.

Intelligent Security and Privacy Features

This camera system is not only smart but also thoughtful. With an optional Blink Subscription Plan (sold separately), you can unlock Person Detection, which uses embedded computer vision to differentiate between a person and other motion, such as a passing animal. This helps minimise unwanted alerts, so you only get notified about what’s truly important. The system also features customisable Privacy Zones, allowing you to block out areas in the camera's view to protect the privacy of your neighbours or other parts of your property, giving you complete control over your surveillance.

Effortless Installation and Seamless Integration

Setting up your Blink Outdoor 4 is a straightforward, wire-free process that takes just minutes, with no professional installation required. Simply insert the included AA lithium batteries and follow the in-app instructions. The Sync Module Core connects to your home's Wi-Fi, allowing the cameras to communicate and store video clips. The system is fully compatible with Alexa, enabling hands-free control and the creation of helpful routines. With the Blink Subscription Plan trial included, you can store and share your video clips in the cloud for up to 30 days, providing an easy way to review and save important moments.

  • Field of View: 143° diagonal

  • Audio: Two-way audio

  • Subscription: Optional Blink Subscription Plan for cloud storage and features like Person Detection (30-day trial included)
  • Compatibility: Works with Alexa, requires iOS 15.0 or Android 9.0 and above

MEET THE LATEST – Blink Outdoor 4 camera is our fourth generation, wireless, smart security camera that helps protect your home inside and out, directly from the Blink app on your smartphone.

SEE, HEAR AND SPEAK FROM THE BLINK APP – Experience 1080p HD live view, infrared night vision and crisp two-way audio.

TWO-YEAR BATTERY LIFE – Set yourself up in minutes and get up to two years of power with the included AA lithium batteries. Additionally, purchase the battery extension pack (sold separately) for up to four years of battery life with each camera.
PRIVACY ZONES – Create up to two Privacy Zones to block out areas in view of your Outdoor

4. Help protect the privacy of neighbours and customise your setup.
ENHANCED MOTION DETECTION – Be alerted to motion faster from your smartphone with dual-zone, enhanced motion detection.

PERSON DETECTION – Get alerts when a person is detected with embedded computer vision (CV) as part of an optional Blink Subscription Plan (sold separately).

SAVE AND SHARE CLIPS – With unlimited storage for up to 30 days. Try it out with a free 30-day trial of the Blink Subscription Plan to store events in the cloud. Sync Module Core included.

IN THE BOX – One camera, one Sync Module Core, two AA lithium metal batteries, one mounting kit, one USB cable and one power adaptor.

Be There from Anywhere with the Newest Generation Blink Camera

The Blink Outdoor 4 is the fourth generation of wireless smart security cameras, offering a significant upgrade in performance and features. Its wider 143° diagonal field of view captures more of your property than its predecessor, providing a more comprehensive view of your surroundings. The camera's enhanced image quality and improved low-light performance ensure you get a clearer picture both day and night. With the included Sync Module Core, this two-camera system gives you the foundation for a complete home security setup, all controlled from the intuitive Blink app on your smartphone.

Intelligent Security and Privacy Features

This camera system is not only smart but also thoughtful. With an optional Blink Subscription Plan (sold separately), you can unlock Person Detection, which uses embedded computer vision to differentiate between a person and other motion, such as a passing animal. This helps minimise unwanted alerts, so you only get notified about what’s truly important. The system also features customisable Privacy Zones, allowing you to block out areas in the camera's view to protect the privacy of your neighbours or other parts of your property, giving you complete control over your surveillance.

Effortless Installation and Seamless Integration

Setting up your Blink Outdoor 4 is a straightforward, wire-free process that takes just minutes, with no professional installation required. Simply insert the included AA lithium batteries and follow the in-app instructions. The Sync Module Core connects to your home's Wi-Fi, allowing the cameras to communicate and store video clips. The system is fully compatible with Alexa, enabling hands-free control and the creation of helpful routines. With the Blink Subscription Plan trial included, you can store and share your video clips in the cloud for up to 30 days, providing an easy way to review and save important moments.

The Shark Stratos is built for your lifestyle. Its flexible wand bends to reach under low-lying furniture, making it easy to clean those hard-to-reach spots without bending over. Relax, it's tagged

Not lost. Nearby

Music streaming services via built-in Wi-Fi
Experience everything from podcasts to internet radio in stunning high definition. Or stream music through AirPlay, Alexa Multi-Room Music (MRM), Chromecast built-in™, and Spotify Connect and leave the room or take a call without the music being interrupted. Retro style meets cutting-edge performance
Make a statement with powerful sound and distinctive retro style. The JBL Authentics 200 speaker recalls JBL’s iconic ‘70s styles—featuring a Quadrex grille, custom leather-like enclosure, and premium aluminum frame, now with even better performance and versatility. Inspired by retro design
The JBL Authentics 200 is inspired by classic JBL heritage designs for a look that complements any room and fills any space—big or small—with superior JBL sound. And the speaker's premium aluminum frame, custom leather-like enclosure, and reimagined Quadrex grille really show the attention we paid to each visual detail, right down to the JBL signature pattern surrounding the down firing passive radiator.

Powerful JBL Pro Sound with AI Sound Boost
How does the already great JBL Charge sound profile get even better? It helps that we have some of the best engineers in the game retooling our kit to deliver our most realistic sound reproduction yet. Wouldn't it be great to share the vibes with our tribe? Now we can. With Auracast™, we can effortlessly stereo pair two Charge 6 speakers for a wider sound stage and connect multiple Auracast™-enabled JBL speakers to cover more ground with the same playlist.
